LanguageData.ARA_Incubator_Nutrient_Solution.label: Arachne nutrient solution
LanguageData.ARA_Incubator_Nutrient_Solution.descript: The nutrient solution of the Arachne Zerg hatching tank, eggs and cocoons all need this liquid rich in various nutrients to maintain the progress of hatching. The cocoon will consume nutrient solution during the hatching process, and Zerg must refill the nutrient solution regularly.
